msgid "Paint Program"
msgstr "Programma per pinger"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kolourpaint.appdata.xml:13
msgid ""
"KolourPaint is a simple painting program to quickly create raster images. It "
"is useful as a touch-up tool and for simple image editing tasks."
msgstr ""
"KolourPant es un simple programma per pinger o designar  per crear "
"rapidemente imagines raster. Il es utile como instrumento de retocco e per "
"cargas simplice de modificar imagines."

